edu.iastate.ansci.flip.database

Class LocalVariablesDB

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iastate.ansci.flip.database.LocalVariablesDB

  • public class LocalVariablesDB
extends java.lang.Object
    Store parameters chosen by an instructor to setup a population. The methods of this class are used by an online instructor. Data is retrieved from temporal database. Index of each parameter:
    - KNOWN_LOCI = 2
    - UNKNOWN_LOCI = 3
    - ENVIRONMENTAL_VARIANCES = 4
    - SWITCHBOX_TYPE = 5
    - BREED = 6
    - NUM_ANIMALS = 7
    - DUAL_SPIN = 8
    Author:
    Patricio Galdames
